              Unlike its predecessors, JPEG&nbsp;XL delivers best-of-breed lossless compression making pixel-precision smaller than ever &mdash; at up to 32 bits per channel. It handily beats WebP on complex content without the 8-bit and size limitations. AVIF? Not even close.
